i		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i- (2022-01)		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iLooking Glass may miss a few keystrokes from time to time;		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i- (2023-05) The latest Looking Glass can relay keyboard and mouse		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
ievents
reliably now.		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
