iGet Audio Output from VM		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i(2023-05) The latest Looking Glass can relay audio now. These steps		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iare kept for
reference only.		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iWhile Virt-Manager can connect to the VM with SPICE protocol to get		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
ithe VM's
sound output, Looking Glass also relays keyboard and mouse		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
ievents through SPICE.
Since the VM only accepts one simultaneous SPICE		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iconnection, we cannot get the
audio output with Virt-Manager.		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
i		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iWe can install		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
hScream	URL:https://github.com/duncanthrax/scream	{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
