imouse
combo, you can pass them into the VM and use them specifically		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
ifor it. USB
passthrough to VM is a mature technology, so the chance of		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
irunning into
problems is very low.		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
